director
for
Sperry
in
Clearwater
,
Fla.
,
admitted
participating
in
a
scheme
to
bribe
Garland
Tomlin
,
the
Navy
official
.
###
Mr.
Tomlin
,
who
left
the
Navy
in
1985
,
pleaded
guilty
earlier
this
year
to
related
conspiracy
,
bribery
and
tax-evasion
charges
.
###
The
bribery
scheme
took
place
between
1982
and
1985
,
according
to
documents
filed
by
prosecutors
in
connection
with
Mr.
Lavelle
's
guilty
plea
in
federal
district
court
in
Alexandria
,
Va
.
###
Sperry
merged
with
Burroughs
Corp.
to
become
Unisys
Corp.
in
late
1986
.
###
Court
documents
filed
by
prosecutors
indicate
Mr.
Tomlin
tried
to
steer
to
Sperry
a
multimillion
dollar
contract
to
