equiment
.
###
Mr.
Tomlin
,
among
other
things
,
illegally
provided
Mr.
Lavelle
with
inside
information
and
documents
intended
to
give
Sperry
an
unfair
advantage
in
the
competition
,
the
documents
said
.
###
Sperry
ultimately
was
eliminated
from
