a
while
.
###
If
he
sponsored
a
contest
on
how
a
bureaucrat
mishandled
something
,
Mr.
Lesko
admits
,
``
I
'd
get
5,000
entries
.
''
###
Now
there
's
an
idea
.
###
Ford
Motor
Co.
and
