to
be
surprised
that
Fidel
does
n't
invite
the
U.S.
State
Department
to
violate
the
jurisdiction
of
the
Cuban
government
over
its
own
territory
.
###
We
badly
need
to
follow
fact
rather
than
the
rhetoric
of
conventional
wisdom
.
###
Without
this
basic
level
of
attention
to
reality
,
our
policies
on
Cuba
will
continue
to
be
as
counterproductive
as
they
have
for
30
