has
grown
among
European
carriers
.
###
``
We
think
alliances
are
very
important
,
''
Mr.
Eddington
says
.
###
``
But
we
'd
rather
put
funds
into
our
own
business
rather
than
someone
else
's
.
###
I
'm
not
sure
cross-ownership
would
necessarily
make
things
smoother
.
''
###
In
a
pattern
it
aims
to
copy
in
